---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SideDrawer from '../components/SideDrawer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Methodology & Services | SPS" description="Our 3-Phase Doctrine: Vetting, Training, and Deployment. How SPS delivers 'Zero Error' security operations.">
  <SideDrawer />
  
  <section class="brutalist-section pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="brutalist-container pl-20">
      <h1 class="text-heading-1 text-primary-accent mb-6">THE METHODOLOGY</h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-body max-w-3xl mb-16 leading-relaxed">
        We do not just supply guards; we engineer security ecosystems. Our "Zero Error" doctrine is built on three non-negotiable pillars.
      </p>

      <!-- Phase 1: Vetting -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 mb-24 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-24">
        <div>
          <span class="text-compliance font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">PHASE 01 // EXTRACTION</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">RADICAL VETTING</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            In an industry rife with fake IDs and unverified migrants, SPS operates a military-grade filtration system. We reject 68% of applicants.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
             <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
               <span class="text-compliance font-bold">01.</span>
               <span class="text-neutral-300"><strong>The 'Native' Check:</strong> We do not rely on local Rent Agreements. We physically verify the applicant's permanent village address via our rural network.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
               <span class="text-compliance font-bold">02.</span>
               <span class="text-neutral-300"><strong>Psychometric Profiling:</strong> Candidates for high-value sectors (Jewellery, Schools) undergo a 'Dark Triad' test to screen for aggression and impulsivity.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
               <span class="text-compliance font-bold">03.</span>
               <span class="text-neutral-300"><strong>Digital Forensic:</strong> We screen public social media profiles for radicalisation or affiliation with political unrest groups.</span>
             </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="brutalist-card bg-neutral-900 flex items-center justify-center">
           <div class="text-center">
             <div class="text-6xl font-mono text-compliance mb-4">68%</div>
             <p class="text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Rejection Rate</p>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2: Training -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 mb-24 border-b border-neutral-800 pb-24">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 brutalist-card bg-neutral-900 flex items-center justify-center">
           <div class="text-center">
             <div class="text-6xl font-mono text-success mb-4">45</div>
             <p class="text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">Days Bootcamp</p>
           </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <span class="text-success font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">PHASE 02 // CALIBRATION</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">THE COMMANDO COURSE</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            A uniform does not make a guard. Training does. Our 45-day residential training program transforms civilians into operators.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
             <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
               <span class="text-success font-bold">01.</span>
               <span class="text-neutral-300"><strong>Firefighting (Live):</strong> Not a PowerPoint presentation. Every recruit must extinguish a Class-B oil fire using a DCP extinguisher.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
               <span class="text-success font-bold">02.</span>
               <span class="text-neutral-300"><strong>Legal Power:</strong> Training on BNS Sections 34-44 (Right of Private Defence). Our guards know exactly when they can legally use force.</span>
             </li>
             <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
               <span class="text-success font-bold">03.</span>
               <span class="text-neutral-300"><strong>Soft Skills:</strong> 'Concierge Security' training for hospitality and corporate deployments. "Firm but Polite."</span>
             </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3: Deployment -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div>
          <span class="text-primary-accent font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">PHASE 03 // EXECUTION</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white mb-6">INTELLIGENCE-LED DEPLOYMENT</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We do not "fill a spot". We deploy a counter-measure.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900">
               <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The Site Survey</h3>
               <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Before a quote is generated, our Intelligence Team conducts a 48-hour threat assessment of your perimeter, identifying blind spots your previous agency missed.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 border border-neutral-800 bg-neutral-900">
               <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The 'QRT' Umbrella</h3>
               <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400">Every deployment is geofenced within the response radius of our mobile Quick Response Teams. Help is never more than 15 minutes away.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="brutalist-card bg-neutral-900 flex flex-col justify-center p-12">
           <h3 class="text-heading-3 mb-6">READY TO UPGRADE?</h3>
           <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8">Move from 'Manpower' to 'Intelligence'.</p>
           <a href="/contact" class="brutalist-button brutalist-button--primary text-center">
             INITIATE AUDIT
           </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work: Consultation Process -->
  <section class="brutalist-section py-24 bg-neutral-950 border-t border-neutral-800">
    <div class="brutalist-container pl-20">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-primary-accent font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">ENGAGEMENT PROTOCOL</span>
        <h2 class="text-heading-2 mb-4">HOW WE WORK</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-neutral-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          From initial contact to operational deployment, here's what to expect when you engage SPS.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 -ml-4 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black">1</div>
          <div class="brutalist-card bg-neutral-900 border-neutral-800 pt-12 h-full">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Initial Contact</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-4">
              Submit your requirements via our secure form or call our Command Centre directly.
            </p>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-compliance">
              Response: Within 4 hours
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 -ml-4 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black">2</div>
          <div class="brutalist-card bg-neutral-900 border-neutral-800 pt-12 h-full">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Site Survey</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-4">
              Our Intelligence Team conducts a comprehensive threat assessment of your premises.
            </p>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-compliance">
              Duration: 24-48 hours
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 -ml-4 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black">3</div>
          <div class="brutalist-card bg-neutral-900 border-neutral-800 pt-12 h-full">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Custom Proposal</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-4">
              Receive a detailed security plan with deployment strategy, costs, and SLA guarantees.
            </p>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-compliance">
              Delivery: Within 72 hours
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 -ml-4 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-accent flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black">4</div>
          <div class="brutalist-card bg-neutral-900 border-neutral-800 pt-12 h-full">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">Deployment</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-4">
              Trained personnel deployed with full documentation, uniforms, and Command Centre integration.
            </p>
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-success">
              Status: Operational
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="brutalist-button brutalist-button--primary">
          START THE PROCESS
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
